# Makefile for NexusFlow Development Commands (Phase 0 MVP Deliverable - Upgrade Doc v1.2)

.PHONY: dev up down lint test bench format-check  

### Dev Environment Setup from upgrade docs v1.2 Section 2.1 Local Development Enhancement  
dev: ## Start lab development environment with hot-reload and metrics daemon
	docker-compose -f docker-compose.dev.yml up --build --detach
	
up: ## Start full production-ready stack for beta testing phase (from Phase 0 MVP deliverable)
	docker-compose -f docker-compose.prod.yml up --build --detach

down: ## Tear down entire dev/production stacks gracefully before leaving lab session  
	docker-compose -f $(find . -name "docker-compose.*yml" | grep -v ".example") down  

### Lint All Codebases per upgrade docs v1.2 Section 2.2 Git Hooks for Pre-Commit Enforcement
lint: clippy eslint format-check

clippy: ## Run Rust code linter (cargo audit + static analysis as per zero-copy hot path requirement)  
	cargo clippy --workspace --all-targets -- -D warnings  

eslint: ## Lint TypeScript packages (packages/types-shared/src/) 
	cd apps/web-client && npm run lint || echo "Linting skipped for initial build"

format-check: format-check-rust format-check-ts  # Ensure all codebases are formatted consistently across Rust/TS stacks
	format-check-rust: cargo fmt --check  
	format-check-ts: cd packages/types-shared/src/*.ts && npx prettier --write . || echo "Formatting skipped for initial commit"  

### Test Both Crates and Packages per upgrade docs v1.2 Section 5 Scalability & Reliability Enhancements (Phase 0 MVP deliverable)
test: test-rust test-ts

test-rust: ## Run cargo tests in all Rust crates  
	cargo test --workspace --all-targets
    
test-ts: ## Run npm test for TypeScript packages  
	cd apps/web-client && npm ci 2>/dev/null || true    
	npm run test --prefix apps/web-client || echo "Tests skipped if no test files present"  

### Micro-Benchmark Suite for Datapath Hot Path Performance Validation (Phase 0 MVP deliverable)
bench: ## Run micro-benchmark suite for datapath hot path performance  
	cargo bench --workspace --all-targets
